Type: Package
Package: odmind
Title: Calculate Origin-Destination Matrix Accessibility
    Indicators
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Marcel",
           family = "Schonlau",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "marcel.schonlau@hs-bochum.de")
Maintainer: Marcel Schonlau <marcel.schonlau@hs-bochum.de>
Description: Provides functions to create origin-destination
    matrices utilizing the OpenRouteService. Based on those matrices
    several functions for calculating accessibility indicators for point
    data as well as aggregation methods to polygon areas of interest are
    available.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/mschonlau/odmind
